      (a) `type: PlaybookNodeType` (coarse category like 'aiAnalysis') used by the React Flow node renderer, and
      (b) Dataverse `sprk_nodetype` Choice column (6-value) populated via `playbookNodeSync.ts`. R7 collapses
      both into `sprk_executortype` (33-value Choice). The literal `__actionType` was a workaround in legacy
      deploy scripts to inject the specific executor into `sprk_configjson` — that hack also goes away.
    </background>
